ing to it but also from playing it on the piano outside his studies coleman teaches a jazz history course at the jazzschool in berkeley he also performs on piano keyboards and percussion around the bay area and freelances as a music journalist tagged with discovery creativity contact us follow us on twitter make a gift to h&s copyright 1997 2012 stanford university all rights reserved
